OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775131865
OL,3,C'Not our King' graffiti sprayed on
OL,4,Ccathedral ahead of Charles visit
OL,6,FGraffiti saying "Not our King" has
OL,7,Fbeen covered up at St Asaph Cathedral
OL,8,Fin Denbighshire just before Charles is
OL,9,Fdue to attend an Easter service.
OL,11,FThe message was sprayed in red paint
OL,12,Fon the cathedral wall where the Royal
OL,13,FMaundy service is being held in Wales
OL,14,Ffor only the second time in its
OL,15,Fhistory.
