OL,3,C'Not our King' graffiti sprayed on
OL,4,Ccathedral ahead of Charles visit
OL,6,FThe King and Queen are due to attend
OL,7,Fthe service, where Charles will
OL,8,Fpresent gifts to 77 men and 77 women
OL,9,Ffrom Wales and other dioceses across
OL,10,Fthe UK in recognition of outstanding
OL,11,FChristian service and for helping
OL,12,Fpeople in their communities.
OL,14,FThe first recorded Royal Maundy
OL,15,Fservice was held in 1210 by King John
OL,16,Fand commemorates the Last Supper of
OL,17,FJesus Christ, with the distribution of
OL,18,Falms becoming a tradition.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
