PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775131865
OL,3,C'Not our King' graffiti sprayed on
OL,4,Ccathedral ahead of Charles visit
OL,6,FCharles will give recipients two
OL,7,Fpurses - a white purse including a set
OL,8,Fof specially minted silver Maundy
OL,9,Fcoins totalling 77 pennies, to match
OL,10,Fthe King's age, and a red purse
OL,11,Fcontaining a #5 coin marking 100 years
OL,12,Fsince the late Queen's birth and a 50p
OL,13,Fcoin celebrating the 50th anniversary
OL,14,Fof The King's Trust charity.
OL,16,FThe King is traditionally assisted in
OL,17,Fdistributing the Maundy Money by the
OL,18,FLord High Almoner, currently the
OL,19,FBishop of Norwich, the Right Rev
OL,20,FGraham Usher.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
