OL,3,C'Not our King' graffiti sprayed on
OL,4,Ccathedral ahead of Charles visit
OL,6,FThis year's service is the first held
OL,7,Fin Wales since 1982 and will feature
OL,8,Fspecially commissioned music by Welsh
OL,9,Fcomposers and musicians to mark the
OL,10,Foccasion.
OL,12,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,13,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,14,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,15,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
